      "title": "Corona deaths increase",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The deaths which took place the day before yesterday (21) have been confirmed by the Director General of Health Services.",
        "According to a statement issued by the Government Information Department, two men and one woman aged between 30 and 59 years were among the dead."
      ],
